  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8274154">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8274154/" class="title-link">长安之殇</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8274154"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48051798/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48051798-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48051798/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沈一默</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-01-04"
      class="main-meta">2017-01-04 23:22:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8274154_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  “碧玉妆成一树高，万条垂下绿丝绦”这是唐朝诗人贺知章的名句。“忽如一夜春风来，千树万树梨花开”这是岑参的佳作。两位大诗人于一千二百年后的今天，在一本书有了交集，但这交集却并非来自诗词歌赋，反而源自于一场意图颠覆长安的惊天阴谋。  《长安十二时辰》的故事安排与...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8274154/#comments">(12回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">72有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8274154_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8274154_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8300136">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8300136/" class="title-link">最不正经的坏孩子依旧也会是个烂好人</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8300136"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/81527250/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u81527250-13.jpg"></a>
